summary: WADA delegation to visit Moscow Anti-Doping Laboratory on November 28
title: WADA delegation to visit Moscow Anti-Doping Laboratory on November 28
body:
WADA delegation to visit Moscow Anti-Doping Laboratory on November 28

© AP Photo/Alexander Zemlianichenko

BAKU, November 15. /TASS/. A delegation from the World Anti-Doping Agency (WADA) will visit the Moscow Anti-Doping Laboratory on November 28, WADA President Sir Craig Reedie said at the Agency’s Foundation Board Meeting in Azerbaijan’s capital of Baku.

On September 20, the WADA Executive Committee decided to reinstate the Russian Anti-Doping Agency (RUSADA)…
